---
title: Smashed Falafels and Buttery Pesto Orzo with Baby Plum Tomatoes, Rocket and Greek Style Yoghurt
description: Not to be confused with rice, orzo is actually a type of pasta. By cooking the falafels and then baking after smashing them, it turns them into a crispy and crunchy topping for the flavoursome orzo.
